high_descs: Turn around and go near the cabinet.
Take the white cloth from the wardrobe.
Turn around and go to the sink.
Put the cloth into the sink and washed it.
Then take it out from the cabinet.
Put the cloth into the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Washed and Placed the Cloth into the Cabinet.

high_descs: Turn right again turn right to the cabinet.
Take the cloth from the cupboard.
Exit from the room turn left go straight to the sink in the bathroom.
Put the cloth in the sink, pour the water and take the cloth back.
Turn around go straight turn right to the cabinet
Put the cloth in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Take the cloth from the cabinet, clean it, and place it in the cabinet.

high_descs: Open the cabinet, take the white cloth from cabinet, Close the cabinet.
Turn right, towards wall, take right, turn left, leave the room, turn left, move in the corridor,  move straight towards the sink.
Put the cloth inside the sink, wash it, take back the cloth.
Turn around, move straight to the end, take right into the room, move forward, take right towards the cabinet.
Open the cabinet, put the cloth inside the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: To get the cloth from cabinet, wash it in the sink, put inside the another cabinet.
